    "name": "THE AMNIS, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Kaohsiung",
    "detail": "One of the best thing is it’s one of the most updated, most cleanest hotel. The room is spacious, comfortable and all the amenities and bed is fresh and new (for now). However, everything comes with a price, which the cost of per night per stay is high. Compared to other 5 stars hotel, this one is probably one of the best in Kaohsiung and other ones are very dated and old. If your finding a top notched 5 star hotel. This is one of them! Facilities like gym, sauna, hot whirlpool and pool are very clean and well maintained. I would’ve go back there again if I had the chance again. And one tip, next to the hotel there is one popular temple, you can visit that one if you have the chance! :) cheers! ",
